pullrpms - Build an RPM repository from transitively resolved dependencies 

The pullrpms utility creates (or adds to) an RPM repository using the
transitive closure of the RPMs and/or RPM requirements specified on the
command line.

Home page: http://pullrpms.googlecode.com/

See INSTALL for installation instructions. After installing, see the pullrpms(8)
man page for how to run it.

See COPYING for license.

See CHANGES for change history.

Enjoy!

